{"tid":1905343,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"停止失敗論 打好每一條戰線 各自努力","createTime":"2020-03-01T07:52:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-06T12:42:07.000Z","uid":147376,"like":68,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"5294909115851ffd1244f174b0812ada95afed5e","tid":1905343,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T07:52:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">停止失敗論 打好每一條戰線 各自努力<br />\n<br />\n你相信制度可以延遲香港沉淪嘅速度 換取時間嚟抗爭 就去做<br />\n<br />\n你相信街頭抗爭可以打擊政權 畀政權壓力 就去做<br />\n<br />\n你相信黃色經濟圈可以成功 阻止商界赤化 就去做<br />\n<br />\n你相信資訊戰網絡戰可以拉攏更多中立甚至對家嘅人加入我哋 同埋鞏固淺黃嘅人 就去做<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>相信上面全部都有用嘅 就全部一齊做！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n你相信嘅方法都盡力去做 唔好理身邊嘅人點睇死你<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山 各自努力<br />\n全民抗共 香港獨立<br />\n<br />\n我講嘢係咁多<br />\n<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"af82c351e966df2c32fbe18a899e48cc1b97b6e7","tid":1905343,"uid":147376,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T07:52:58.000Z","msg":"幫我推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce840b3da8dfd10e0e18c2d855f7df8a3dcd6e2e","tid":1905343,"uid":19278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T07:53:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e560da5242abe8e1721895eddf6fa3f1d4486f6d","tid":1905343,"uid":147376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T07:53:20.000Z","msg":"人心從未冷卻 冷卻嘅 係你自己"},{"pid":"f9a0c0c6cf77ff3f26d0880fd18903cb7bc10fa7","tid":1905343,"uid":147376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T07:54:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">街頭戰<br />\n資訊戰<br />\n制度戰<br />\n國際戰<br />\n<br />\n同時進行 同樣重要 缺一不可 </span></strong></span>"},{"pid"